            <h3>Critical Issues (Immediate Action Required)</h3>
            <div class="vulnerability-list">
                <div class="vulnerability-item">
                    <div class="vulnerability-title">Administrative Interface Exposure</div>
                    <p><strong>Impact:</strong> Complete server compromise, data theft, service disruption</p>
                    <p><strong>Likelihood:</strong> High - Easily discoverable and commonly targeted</p>
