            <ul>
                <li><strong>TLS/SSL Analysis:</strong> Configuration analysis failed due to internal tool errors</li>
                <li><strong>CDN Detection:</strong> Unable to determine Content Delivery Network usage</li>
                <li><strong>Directory Enumeration:</strong> Limited due to wordlist access restrictions</li>
                <li><strong>HTTP Service Analysis:</strong> Incomplete due to tool limitations</li>
                <li><strong>Scope:</strong> External assessment only - internal network not evaluated</li>
                <li><strong>Time-bound:</strong> Point-in-time assessment - security posture may change</li>
