        <!-- Conclusion -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>üìù Conclusion</h2>
            <p>The security assessment of him-shakti.com reveals significant security vulnerabilities that require immediate attention. The extensive subdomain exposure, particularly of administrative and email services, presents serious risks to the organization's digital infrastructure and data security.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Priority Actions:</strong></p>
            <ol>
                <li>Immediately secure administrative interfaces with access controls</li>
                <li>Implement strong authentication on all email services</li>
                <li>Review and restrict access to file storage systems</li>
                <li>Deploy comprehensive monitoring and alerting systems</li>
                <li>Develop and implement incident response procedures</li>
            </ol>
            
            <p>Regular security assessments and continuous monitoring are essential to maintain a strong security posture in the evolving threat landscape.</p>
